### API Testing File for Product, Customer, and Order CRUD Operations
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ===== PRODUCT CRUD OPERATIONS =====

### Create a new product
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "price": 999.99
}

### Create another product
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mouse",
  "price": 29.99
}

### Get all products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### Get a specific product (replace with actual product ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1

### Update a product (replace with actual product ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Laptop",
  "price": 1099.99
}

### Delete a product (replace with actual product ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/1

### ===== CUSTOMER CRUD OPERATIONS =====

