Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "address": "123 Main St, New York, NY 10001"
}

### Create another customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/customer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "address": "456 Oak Ave, Los Angeles, CA 90001"
}

### Note: Based on the code analysis, the customer service only has a Create endpoint implemented.
### Additional CRUD operations (Get, Update, Delete, List) would need to be implemented in the customer service.

